{"tid":1323850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"置頂！[升級版遍地開花行動計劃] 圍堵18區政府合署!!!","createTime":"2019-07-16T11:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T12:02:48.000Z","uid":76219,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d517fde7ebd5c7268a9f84bdc4b3a796e2cd665f","tid":1323850,"uid":76219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:29:24.000Z","msg":"首先想講我地而家要穩固軍心要做嘅野係集中講五大訴求：<br />\n 1. 全面撤回「送中」惡法<br />\n 2. 收回暴動定性<br />\n 3. 追究警隊濫權<br />\n 4. 撤銷義士控罪<br />\n 5. 林鄭下台，實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遍地開花為圍堵18區政府合署，入去宣讀五大訴求！<br />\n圍堵政府合署 比到政府一個徹徹底底嘅合理壓力迫政府正面回應，如同以前税務大樓事件同一性質。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如有同見者行動前必需做好評估分析，設定徹退路線。如遇到包圍，圍捕情況，務必跟徹退路線齊上齊落，殺出重圍，以防有更多義士被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">最近大家都被警犬模糊咗焦點<br />\n令每次行動都變得漫無目的同埋意義不大，最後只會令當權者達到目的。<br />\n為咗避免呢種情況發生，我請求各位要清醒，黑警係仆街，但更仆街嘅係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當權者</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我們勢不低頭，勇戰到底<br />\n不分化，不割蓆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ccbec50a21f30f3c2819abfff2e075fd1db19ee","tid":1323850,"uid":47222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:29:55.000Z","msg":"推左721先再講啦屌"},{"pid":"d80d7c878207d70a942d93e561fccdb48f1d3916","tid":1323850,"uid":76219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:30:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ebddea204dbffeb3bce6e9f1252691fad770aab","tid":1323850,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ccbec50a21f30f3c2819abfff2e075fd1db19ee","tid":1323850,"uid":47222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:29:55.000Z","msg":"推左721先再講啦屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:30:31.000Z","msg":"完"},{"pid":"b94c8098295eedc6e8d78ff09f71f8f5099154eb","tid":1323850,"uid":76219,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0ccbec50a21f30f3c2819abfff2e075fd1db19ee","tid":1323850,"uid":47222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:29:55.000Z","msg":"推左721先再講啦屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:32:05.000Z","msg":"遍地開花 各區都要幫手<br />\n721係遊行而已，雖然之後會發生咩事無人知"},{"pid":"1602e4057e11fc0744c435a70c0b886419d021aa","tid":1323850,"uid":76219,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4ebddea204dbffeb3bce6e9f1252691fad770aab","tid":1323850,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ccbec50a21f30f3c2819abfff2e075fd1db19ee","tid":1323850,"uid":47222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:29:55.000Z","msg":"推左721先再講啦屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:30:31.000Z","msg":"完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:37:13.000Z","msg":"完乜撚嘢，以家比多啲人知道有呢個計劃可以去做，好過坐以待斃<br />\n你知唔知以家好多人都一路吹灰，又或者灰咗<br />\n原因係覺得近期嘅行動好<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">漫無目的</span></span><br />\n而你要人地衝大部分人都唔敢，政府要模糊世界所有人嘅視線，令佢地集中討論警民衝突<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">到時候五大訴求就真係壽終正寢架啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"fd248ac761ec3b1aa93c943f6f8adbc0dd98abbe","tid":1323850,"uid":76219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:41:53.000Z","msg":"以家係<span style=\"color: red;\">無誘因/誘因唔夠大</span>令香港人再出嚟呀<br />\n所以我地要重新檢視行動，做有目的，亦有意義嘅行動<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">最理想係好似7.1佔領立法會咁，佔領到18區政府合署為求宣讀五大訴求</span></span>，真正達致<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">遍地開花</span>"},{"pid":"2db10a48826cf9358949bc3407aac9af3b4ad5d8","tid":1323850,"uid":53714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:49:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a645b69d34abafbb67fb9595271755a16293f614","tid":1323850,"uid":53714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:02:48.000Z","msg":"推呀"}]}